          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has browned, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>,<strong> chopped ginger</strong>, <strong>spring onion batons </strong>and <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>pepper</strong> to the pan and cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to soften and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1695721359251-x200.jpg",
